PRIMARY PURPOSE
Reporting to the Quality Control Supervisor, the Quality Control Technician is responsible for the routine collection/testing of materials, as well as the adherence of all testing methods.
RESPONSIBILITIES
Conduct routine and situational analysis of materials;
Compile all reports in a timely and accurate manner
Communicate test results in a timely manner to the QC Supervisor and properly document in database;
Ensure housekeeping standards are maintained in and around the lab;

